  <brief_title>EFFECT OF PRE EXTUBATION MANUAL HYPERINFLATION TECHNIQUE VS REGULAR EXTUBATION AFTER STERNOTOMY</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Pre-extubation Manual Hyper Inflation in Comparison to Regular Extubation Following Sternotomy.</official_title>
